{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Psa|99","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","chapter":99,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:99:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":99,"verse":1,"text":"The Lord reigns! Let the peoples tremble. He is enthroned between the cherubim. Let the earth quake.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:99:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":99,"verse":2,"text":"The Lord is great in Zion; he is exalted above all the peoples.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:99:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":99,"verse":3,"text":"Let them praise your great and awe-inspiring name. He is holy.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:99:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":99,"verse":4,"text":"The mighty King loves justice. You have established fairness; you have administered justice and righteousness in Jacob.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:99:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":99,"verse":5,"text":"Exalt the Lord our God; bow in worship at his footstool. He is holy.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:99:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":99,"verse":6,"text":"Moses and Aaron were among his priests; Samuel also was among those calling on his name. They called to the Lord and he answered them.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:99:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":99,"verse":7,"text":"He spoke to them in a pillar of cloud; they kept his decrees and the statutes he gave them.","